Simple To-Do List Web App

A minimal task manager web application built with HTML, CSS, and JavaScript. Users can add, complete, and delete tasks, and their tasks are saved locally using localStorage.

Features

Add new tasks quickly.

Mark tasks as completed by clicking on them.

Delete tasks easily.

Tasks are stored in the browser using localStorage so they persist between sessions.

Responsive and simple design, works on desktop and mobile screens.

Technologies Used

HTML

CSS

JavaScript

localStorage (for saving tasks)